Tkx-FindBar
===========

This module defines a Perl Tkx megawidget that provides a toolbar for 
incremental searching of a Tk text widget.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

  Perl 5.006
  Tkx

